{"tid":1708344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［1111］淺黃有感","createTime":"2019-11-11T14:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T15:28:27.000Z","uid":282115,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba24522fad38f74f9abb0f244dad21e9f238aeed","tid":1708344,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:24:00.000Z","msg":"首先利申左先<br />\n淺黃<br />\n每星期一兩次出席活動<br />\n但離遠見到popo就好驚會退走<br />\n但又用公司資源印文宣派<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今朝早我罷左工<br />\n去巴士站做排隊黨<br />\n企係個站比成十個手足屌左兩個鐘港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個人感覺就係有一堆前線啲既手足被分化風感染到<br />\n有勇武割和理既趨勢<br />\n<br />\n特徵係忍受唔到淺黃partime 抗爭<br />\n覺得排隊返工既人十惡不赦無良知<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">但大波man經過時就得返兩個手足敢屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n計我話<br />\n對淺藍淺黃好言相勸絕對比屌到反皮好<br />\n對深藍就緊係屌啦唔洗教下麻<br />\n但無理由調返轉咼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">正確「你睇幾長龍？影張相同公司講返唔到啦」<br />\n<br />\n錯誤「死左人喇仲返工」<br />\n「屌得你岩驚柒唔敢走呀？」<br />\n「咁鐘意返工？行路返啦屌你老母」</span>"},{"pid":"77ddf60eea7e2acda7160527a2840ae858d79758","tid":1708344,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:25:42.000Z","msg":"收皮啦分化p牌五毛仔<br />\n我係和理，勇武同我割我都攬住佢大肶唔備佢走"},{"pid":"9755d7b3b3e241069585f33c1f28437683b83653","tid":1708344,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77ddf60eea7e2acda7160527a2840ae858d79758","tid":1708344,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:25:42.000Z","msg":"收皮啦分化p牌五毛仔<br />\n我係和理，勇武同我割我都攬住佢大肶唔備佢走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇左文未<br />\n<br />\n我咁都分化p牌五毛仔？"},{"pid":"18e3f4bfe2b79e586f66ca05ef8b1797147716ac","tid":1708344,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"可以友善少少<br />\n無人鐘意俾人屌係事實"},{"pid":"3ab2b081042ba6781ae73cbd903bbe62b0dc0c9f","tid":1708344,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:50:07.000Z","msg":"我為你擋子彈，<br />\n你今日 罷工 可以嗎？"},{"pid":"7351da1dd2112726a856e944aa3ee104d0623530","tid":1708344,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ab2b081042ba6781ae73cbd903bbe62b0dc0c9f","tid":1708344,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:50:07.000Z","msg":"我為你擋子彈，<br />\n你今日 罷工 可以嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:27:16.000Z","msg":"佢去做排隊黨 唔係返工<br />\n咁樣俾人屌又真係灰既"},{"pid":"9a1335af30569ad4ea86f3854883bea1d5418470","tid":1708344,"uid":143435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"各有各做, 記得我地既初衷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}